description: Lists model compilation jobs that satisfy various filters. To create a model compilation job, use CreateCompilationJob. To get information about a particular model compilation job you have created, use DescribeCompilationJob.

nested_items.name: CompilationJobSummaries
nested_items.description: An array of CompilationJobSummary objects, each describing a model compilation job.

nested_items.name: CompilationJobName
nested_items.description: The name of the model compilation job that you want a summary for.

nested_items.name: CompilationJobArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the model compilation job.

nested_items.name: CreationTime
nested_items.description: The time when the model compilation job was created.

nested_items.name: CompilationStartTime
nested_items.description: The time when the model compilation job started.

nested_items.name: CompilationEndTime
nested_items.description: The time when the model compilation job completed.

nested_items.name: CompilationTargetDevice
nested_items.description: The type of device that the model will run on after the compilation job has completed.

nested_items.name: CompilationTargetPlatformOs
nested_items.description: The type of OS that the model will run on after the compilation job has completed.

nested_items.name: CompilationTargetPlatformArch
nested_items.description: The type of architecture that the model will run on after the compilation job has completed.

nested_items.name: CompilationTargetPlatformAccelerator
nested_items.description: The type of accelerator that the model will run on after the compilation job has completed.

nested_items.name: LastModifiedTime
nested_items.description: The time when the model compilation job was last modified.

nested_items.name: CompilationJobStatus
nested_items.description: The status of the model compilation job.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: If the response is truncated, Amazon SageMaker AI returns this NextToken. To retrieve the next set of model compilation jobs, use this token in the next request.
